title: Garden Fresh Tour Visits Battery Park, NYC
description: Mrs. Meyer's Clean Day visited the Battery Conservancy Harvest Festival in New York City for local honey tasting, music, games and seeing little gardeners get inspired. Festival goers stopped by to say hello and wash up at our sinks with their favorite garden-fresh scent. Happy Harvesting!
